                     <interp inst="t18441021-2577-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18441021-2577-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 2 spoons, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18441021-name-1077" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18441021-name-1077" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
